  "title": "Executive, Exhibitor Services (Exhibitions & Events)",
  "description": "<p><strong>A Day in the Life:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Correspond with international exhibitors via email or tele-conversations</p></li><li><p>Collate exhibitors' orders</p></li><li><p>Process payments and collections</p></li><li><p>Assist the Project Manager in coordinating pre-site and event site matters</p></li><li><p>Assist the project team with administrative duties</p></li><li><p>Liaise with exhibitors regarding booth requirements</p></li><li><p>Brief orders to suppliers</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Are Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma holder in Tourism / Events Management or equivalent</p></li><li><p>1 to 2 years of relevant experience</p></li><li><p>Well-versed in Microsoft Word / Excel / Project</p></li></ul>",
